title: Vin Diesel Reveals 'Fast & Furious 8' Is Headed To 'New York, Baby!'
text: Vin Diesel is all smiles as he makes an appearance on The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon on Wednesday (October 14) in New York City. The 48-year-old actor shared a adorable photo of his baby girl Pauline and revealed new details about his upcoming film Fast & Furious 8. PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics [...] Â»
